{"segments": [{"Time_Start": 0.0, "Time_End": 7.0, "Text": " Anybody want to try?"}, {"Time_Start": 7.0, "Time_End": 12.0, "Text": " Anyone who want to try?"}, {"Time_Start": 12.0, "Time_End": 17.0, "Text": " Anyone at all?"}, {"Time_Start": 17.0, "Time_End": 22.0, "Text": " I'm going to ask one more time, and then I'm going to let the show start."}, {"Time_Start": 22.0, "Time_End": 32.0, "Text": " Were you a math major, sir?"}, {"Time_Start": 32.0, "Time_End": 34.0, "Text": " Physics."}, {"Time_Start": 34.0, "Time_End": 36.0, "Text": " Stand up, sir."}, {"Time_Start": 36.0, "Time_End": 41.0, "Text": " Come on up on stage, sir."}, {"Time_Start": 41.0, "Time_End": 43.0, "Text": " Come on up."}, {"Time_Start": 43.0, "Time_End": 45.0, "Text": " You too, sir."}, {"Time_Start": 45.0, "Time_End": 49.0, "Text": " Ask your questions."}, {"Time_Start": 49.0, "Time_End": 51.0, "Text": " Ask your questions."}, {"Time_Start": 52.0, "Time_End": 55.0, "Text": " Where did you go to school?"}, {"Time_Start": 55.0, "Time_End": 56.0, "Text": " Sorry?"}, {"Time_Start": 56.0, "Time_End": 58.0, "Text": " Where did you go to school?"}, {"Time_Start": 58.0, "Time_End": 60.0, "Text": " Where did you go to school?"}, {"Time_Start": 60.0, "Time_End": 62.0, "Text": " Here, you ask me, I'll ask him."}, {"Time_Start": 62.0, "Time_End": 64.0, "Text": " We have a translation problem here."}, {"Time_Start": 64.0, "Time_End": 66.0, "Text": " English is not his first language."}, {"Time_Start": 66.0, "Time_End": 69.0, "Text": " Where did you go to school?"}, {"Time_Start": 69.0, "Time_End": 70.0, "Text": " Where did you go to university?"}, {"Time_Start": 70.0, "Time_End": 72.0, "Text": " Williams and Penn."}, {"Time_Start": 72.0, "Time_End": 74.0, "Text": " What branch of physics?"}, {"Time_Start": 74.0, "Time_End": 76.0, "Text": " What branch of physics?"}, {"Time_Start": 76.0, "Time_End": 77.0, "Text": " High energy."}, {"Time_Start": 77.0, "Time_End": 78.0, "Text": " High energy physics."}, {"Time_Start": 78.0, "Time_End": 81.0, "Text": " Would this be, have your"}, {"Time_Start": 81.0, "Time_End": 82.0, "Text": " have your work work?"}, {"Time_Start": 82.0, "Time_End": 85.0, "Text": " worked at a national lab before?"}, {"Time_Start": 85.0, "Time_End": 86.0, "Text": " Brookhaven."}, {"Time_Start": 86.0, "Time_End": 87.0, "Text": " Brookhaven National Labs."}, {"Time_Start": 87.0, "Time_End": 90.0, "Text": " I was also over at CERN for a few years."}, {"Time_Start": 90.0, "Time_End": 92.0, "Text": " And CERN."}, {"Time_Start": 92.0, "Time_End": 94.0, "Text": " So is this as a civilian contractor?"}, {"Time_Start": 94.0, "Time_End": 96.0, "Text": " Yeah."}, {"Time_Start": 96.0, "Time_End": 98.0, "Text": " Did you ever have like that?"}, {"Time_Start": 98.0, "Time_End": 101.0, "Text": " Did you ever have an idea?"}, {"Time_Start": 101.0, "Time_End": 106.0, "Text": " High energy physics money comes from the federal government,"}, {"Time_Start": 106.0, "Time_End": 107.0, "Text": " generally speaking."}, {"Time_Start": 107.0, "Time_End": 111.0, "Text": " So in that sense, yeah, I was getting money from the federal government"}, {"Time_Start": 111.0, "Time_End": 112.0, "Text": " very indirectly."}, {"Time_Start": 112.0, "Time_End": 116.0, "Text": " and in those days in very small amounts."}, {"Time_Start": 116.0, "Time_End": 117.0, "Text": " So..."}, {"Time_Start": 117.0, "Time_End": 119.0, "Text": " Did you ever work with the space alien ships at Area 51?"}, {"Time_Start": 119.0, "Time_End": 120.0, "Text": " Nope."}, {"Time_Start": 120.0, "Time_End": 124.0, "Text": " Did you ever do any contracting for the DOE?"}, {"Time_Start": 124.0, "Time_End": 126.0, "Text": " Did you ever contract for the DOE?"}, {"Time_Start": 126.0, "Time_End": 130.0, "Text": " I was way too junior in those days"}, {"Time_Start": 130.0, "Time_End": 134.0, "Text": " to have any idea in detail where the money came from."}, {"Time_Start": 134.0, "Time_End": 137.0, "Text": " So I'm not going to tell you, I don't know."}, {"Time_Start": 137.0, "Time_End": 138.0, "Text": " In terms..."}, {"Time_Start": 138.0, "Time_End": 140.0, "Text": " That's right."}, {"Time_Start": 140.0, "Time_End": 141.0, "Text": " So you work with high energy physics, yes?"}, {"Time_Start": 141.0, "Time_End": 142.0, "Text": " physics, yes?"}, {"Time_Start": 142.0, "Time_End": 143.0, "Text": " Yeah."}, {"Time_Start": 143.0, "Time_End": 145.0, "Text": " Would you work with the optics side of the house?"}, {"Time_Start": 145.0, "Time_End": 146.0, "Text": " No."}, {"Time_Start": 146.0, "Time_End": 148.0, "Text": " Which side of the house are you working at?"}, {"Time_Start": 148.0, "Time_End": 150.0, "Text": " We're doing particle physics."}, {"Time_Start": 150.0, "Time_End": 167.0, "Text": " We published a paper in 74 about the discovery of a particle that had a mass of 3.1 G.E."}, {"Time_Start": 167.0, "Time_End": 170.0, "Text": " How many people here have any idea of what do you say?"}, {"Time_Start": 170.0, "Time_End": 171.0, "Text": " of what do you say?"}, {"Time_Start": 171.0, "Time_End": 175.0, "Text": " Well, our paper called it J, and the other paper called it SIE."}, {"Time_Start": 175.0, "Time_End": 176.0, "Text": " What's that?"}, {"Time_Start": 176.0, "Time_End": 177.0, "Text": " Okay."}, {"Time_Start": 177.0, "Time_End": 181.0, "Text": " For those of you who raised your hands, everybody in the audience, feds."}, {"Time_Start": 181.0, "Time_End": 185.0, "Text": " That was one of those stupid fed questions that I asked, where you can kind of nail them down."}, {"Time_Start": 185.0, "Time_End": 186.0, "Text": " Yes, sir."}, {"Time_Start": 186.0, "Time_End": 187.0, "Text": " Have you played with hands a bit?"}, {"Time_Start": 187.0, "Time_End": 188.0, "Text": " Have you played?"}, {"Time_Start": 188.0, "Time_End": 189.0, "Text": " Nope."}, {"Time_Start": 189.0, "Time_End": 192.0, "Text": " Remember the old adage."}, {"Time_Start": 192.0, "Time_End": 195.0, "Text": " If it bleeds, it's biology."}, {"Time_Start": 195.0, "Time_End": 197.0, "Text": " If it smells bad, it's chemistry."}, {"Time_Start": 197.0, "Time_End": 199.0, "Text": " If it doesn't work, it's physics."}, {"Time_Start": 199.0, "Time_End": 209.0, "Text": " Can you explain Schrodinger's cat theory?"}, {"Time_Start": 209.0, "Time_End": 211.0, "Text": " Nope."}, {"Time_Start": 211.0, "Time_End": 215.0, "Text": " Have you ever worked with a tocomac before?"}, {"Time_Start": 215.0, "Time_End": 218.0, "Text": " Have you ever worked with a tocomac? What the hell is a tocomac?"}, {"Time_Start": 218.0, "Time_End": 219.0, "Text": " Fusion reactor."}, {"Time_Start": 219.0, "Time_End": 222.0, "Text": " No, that was a little bit after I left PPA."}, {"Time_Start": 222.0, "Time_End": 224.0, "Text": " Okay, so three-letter agency."}, {"Time_Start": 224.0, "Time_End": 226.0, "Text": " What, you're reaching?"}, {"Time_Start": 226.0, "Time_End": 228.0, "Text": " No, no, Princeton Penn Accelerator."}, {"Time_Start": 228.0, "Time_End": 229.0, "Text": " He's reaching."}, {"Time_Start": 229.0, "Time_End": 232.0, "Text": " What was the last classified paper you published?"}, {"Time_Start": 232.0, "Time_End": 238.0, "Text": " Since I've never published any of them, it hasn't been published yet."}, {"Time_Start": 238.0, "Time_End": 241.0, "Text": " Is it because they wouldn't let you?"}, {"Time_Start": 241.0, "Time_End": 242.0, "Text": " No."}, {"Time_Start": 242.0, "Time_End": 244.0, "Text": " I'm afraid he's not a fed, ladies and gentlemen."}, {"Time_Start": 244.0, "Time_End": 245.0, "Text": " Sorry."}, {"Time_Start": 245.0, "Time_End": 253.0, "Text": " And we'll go ahead, and just for you, sir, we're going to start the talks."}]}